    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine runs roughly and there are noticeable transmission shifts, suggesting a need for a major overhaul. Externally, the body shows several large dents, patches of rust, and significant paint fading, while the interior has heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This is an ideal project car for someone with mechanical expertise or can serve as a source for parts.",
