    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Unlock the potential of this diamond in the rough! Perfect for a dedicated DIYer or someone looking for a rewarding restoration project, this vehicle is looking for a fresh start. While it currently requires significant mechanical attention and shows considerable wear and tear, it offers a fantastic, low-cost entry point for someone ready to roll up their sleeves and bring it back to its former glory. Sold as-is, it's the ultimate canvas for your next automotive adventure!",
