    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Meticulously maintained and kept in a climate-controlled environment, it retains its original showroom luster with no discernible wear to the interior or exterior surfaces. Every mechanical component and aesthetic detail has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our uncompromising standards for excellence. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a pristine specimen of engineering mastery, offering an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 43800.0,
